    "client_msg_id": "771c960e-e79f-48cd-9544-1979f00532e1",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hi all. I'm a mathematician and computer languages enthusiast, interested in topics going from formal proofs, user interfaces for editing technical documents, manageable and open source software engineering, high-quality computer typography. I'm part of a group of people developing the free scientific editing platform TeXmacs (<http://www.texmacs.org|www.texmacs.org>, <https://twitter.com/gnu_texmacs>) which is a complete solution for scientific document preparation and reproducible science including interactive sessions with external software. I'm here to look for possible collaborations/interactions with other projects which look forward into the evolution of our way to use computers to express, develop and publish ideas.",
    "user": "U021CGJSEN4",
    "ts": "1619970212.156300",
